  "detailed_description": "Very easy to play, very difficult to finish. <strong>Can you finish the World's Hardest Game</strong>?<br><br>The World's Hardest Game, which you used to play on flash game sites, is now with you in 3D. Good luck in this challenging game with 30 unique episodes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 different challenging levels<br></li><li>Long playing time<br></li><li>New levels will be added with updates<br></li><li>Auto save system</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bird's Eye View</h2>You can switch to <strong>Bird's Eye View</strong> to see the entire levelyou are in, but you cannot move while in <strong>Bird's Eye View</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489000/extras/birdeye_gif.gif?t=1675461553\" /></span>",
